name: Jack's B-Day 2016
body:
### Jack's 4th Birthday!
Jack is turning 4 and we want you to join us at Defy Gravity to celebrate.

Friday, April 8th
6:00 to 7:30 pm
@ Defy Gravity

345 Sporting Village Dr Suite #1
Lincoln, NE 68502

*pizza & dessert served at 7:00
*socks, wrist bands will be provided
